quran[10{c,v,t}:
30,6,"yeh wada Allah ne kya hai, Allah kabhi apne waday ki khilaaf warzi nahi karta, magar aksar log nahi jantay hain"
30,7,log duniya ki zindagi ka bas zahiri pehlu jantay hain aur akhirat se woh khud hi ghaafil hain
30,8,kya unhon ne kabhi apne aap mein ghhor o fikar nahi kya? Allah ne zameen aur asmano ko aur unn saari cheezon ko jo unn ke darmain hain barhaq aur aik muqarrar muddat hi ke liye peda kya hai magar bohat se log apne rab ki mulaqaat ke munkir hain
30,9,"aur kya yeh log kabhi zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke aِnhin unn logon ka injaam nazar aata jo inn se pehlay guzar chuke hain? woh inn se ziyada taaqat rakhtay thay, onhon ne zameen ko khoob udehra tha aur ussay itna abad kya tha jitna unhon ne nahi kya hai unn ke paas un ke rasool roshan nishanain le kar aeye phir Allah un par zulm karne wala nah tha, magar woh khud hi apne oopar zulm kar rahay thay"
30,10,"Aakhirkar jin logon ne buraiyan ki theen un ka injaam bohat bura howa, is liye ke unhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhatlaya tha aur woh un ka mazaq uratay thay"
30,11,"Allah hi Khalq ki ibtida karta hai, phir wohi is ka iada kere ga, phir isi ki taraf tum pultayjao ge"
30,12,aur jab woh saa-at barpaa ho gi is din mujrim hook dik reh jayen ge
30,13,un ke tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi un ka sfarshi nah ho ga aur woh apne sharikon ke munkir ho jayen ge
30,14,"jis roz woh saa-at barpaa ho gi, is din ( sab ensaan ) allag garohoon mein Butt jayen ge"
30,15,jo log imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain woh aik baagh mein Shadan o Ferhan rakhay jayen ge
